Drifter data was collected hourly. All dates and times are UTC. Contact Coral Reef Ecosystem Division (CRED), NOAA Pacific Island Fisheries Science Center for more information. http://www.pifsc.noaa.gov/cred/oceanography.php       </abstract>    <purpose>         These data were collected for coral reef ecosystem research.  They are collected concurrently with ecological/biological reef assessments and monitoring data.       </purpose>    <supplinf>         CRED drifter information PTT: 52299 Type: SVP Mfg Model: Drogue
